name: MoveIntoVehicle
documentation:
Puts the latest previously defined human (most likely the one directly above) into the vehicle at the given position at the start of the game.

*WARNING*: Human must be on DoorPoint of the vehicle (the point where the human would enter the vehicle in-game)! Vehicle Coordinates [x,y] => DoorPoint [x-2,y-4]. Also fo not forget to use `attachtovehicle`!
